   <text:p text:style-name="P40"/>
   <text:h text:style-name="P19" text:outline-level="2"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Communication </text:span>コミュニケーション</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="P21" text:outline-level="3"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intra-store 店舗内</text:span></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">If the camera is not mounted in the touchscreen and control enclosure, it will have to communicate its data to the SBC. If the face detection, feature location, and <text:span text:style-name="T8">IR-Face </text:span>vector generation is embedded in the camera, very small data (only the vectors) will be transmitted to the control unit so wireless Bluetooth is feasible. Otherwise, wired Ethernet or wireless WiFi, would need to connect the camera to the control unit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P21" text:outline-level="3"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inter-store </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T11">(Optional Networking)</text:span></text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">店舗間（オプションのネットワーク接続</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P42">Multiple stores in the same chain or franchise can choose to share the <text:span text:style-name="T8">IR-Base</text:span> database amongst themselves. They would communicate via an AWS-based (Amazon Web Services) cloud server (designed by CIRC-CO.com) attached to an Amazon RDS MySQL server.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16">同一チェーンやフランチャイズに属する複数の店舗は、IR-Baseデータベースを相互に共有する運用を選択できます。各店舗間の通信は、Amazon RDS MySQLサーバーに接続されたAWS（Amazon Web Services）ベースのクラウドサーバー（CIRC-CO.comが設計）を介して行われます。</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:span text:style-name="T4"/></text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>